725926f-b.title: Queens: 159th Street - 109th Avenue
725926f-b.text:
159th Street, west side, between 109th and Brinkerhoff
Avenues, showing the Refuge Church of Christ. View 1 shows
the north side; view 2 the south side.
P. L. Sperr  March 30, 1932
NO REPRODUCTUONS
Views 1,2
